<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1434] Font being changed after form field is set</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1434</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have encounter a problem when using pdfbox.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have a pdf form with fields and font set to Courier (please see attached pdf file PRP.pdf).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After running the program TEstbed1.java which tries to set the value of one of the fields, font was being changed to Helvetica (please see attached pdf file forms26916.pdf).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is there any way we can set the values and retain the original font?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Windows XP Professional, java version &amp;quot;1.6.0_37&amp;quot;</environment>
